  "title": "Furniture Warehouse Assistant / Assembler",
  "description": "<p><strong>Furniture Warehouse\nAssistant / Assembler</strong></p><p><em>(Forklift / Stacker\nLicensed)</em></p><p><strong>Salary & Benefits</strong></p><p>• S$2,200 – S$3,000 basic<br />\n• Overtime + team / personal incentives<br />\n• Performance bonus<br />\n• Annual leave 12–18 days<br />\n• Staff free product credit & staff discounts</p><p><strong>Job Scope</strong></p><p>• Warehouse work: loading,\nunloading, packing, stock keeping<br />\n• Operate forklift / stacker / pallet jack<br />\n• Furniture delivery, assembly & installation<br />\n• Basic furniture repair & maintenance<br />\n• Keep warehouse, tools & vehicles clean and safe</p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><p>• Forklift or stacker\nlicence (required)<br />\n• Physically fit, able to carry heavy furniture<br />\n• Experience in warehouse, delivery or furniture work preferred<br />\n• Able to use basic hand & power tools<br />\n• Responsible, punctual, team player</p><p><strong>Work Details</strong></p><p>• 5-day work week (Mon–Sat)<br />\n• 8 hours per day<br />\n• Overtime during peak periods</p><p><strong>中文简介</strong></p><p>• 货仓工作：装卸、拣货、包装<br />\n• 操作叉车 / 堆高机<br />\n• 家具送货、安装、维修<br />\n• 体格强壮，肯学习，守时负责</p>",
